data.text: Uttarakhand Subordinate Service Selection Commission (UKSSSC) is expected to release the official notification for the UKSSSC Stenographer Personal Assistant 2023. A total of 158 vacancies were released for the last recruitment cycle and more vacancies are expected to be released for this year. Candidates who have a Secondary School Certificate are applicable to appear for the exam. The selected candidates will get a salary range between Rs. 25,500 to Rs. 1,124,000. Candidates who want a successful selection can refer to the UKSSSC Stenographer Personal Assistant Previous Year Papers too.
